@startuml sd_EmployeeService_create
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title EmployeeService.create(employee) - 创建员工

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "EmployeeController" as Ctrl
participant "EmployeeService" as Service
participant "EmployeeRepository" as Repo
participant "Employee\n(实体)" as Entity

Client -> Ctrl: POST /api/employees\n{name, employeeNo, hireDate, ...}
Ctrl -> Service: create(employee)
note right of Service : @Transactional
Service -> Repo: save(employee)
Repo --> Service: 持久化后的Employee\n(含ID)
Service --> Ctrl: Employee
note right of Entity : JPA自动生成ID\n关联department\n关联自动生成时间戳
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<Employee>
@enduml
